ration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">la nomina del suddetto Sub-Responsabile, a condizione che:</span></p><ol style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\" start=\"1\"><li style=\"list-style-type:decimal;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Venga sottoscritto un contratto (DPA) che imponga al Sub-Responsabile gli </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>stessi obblighi</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> di protezione dati previsti nel contratto tra noi in essere.</span></p></li><li style=\"list-style-type:decimal;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Qualora il Sub-Responsabile ometta di adempiere ai propri obblighi, Lei rimarrà integralmente responsabile nei nostri confronti per l&#039;inadempimento di tale soggetto.</span></p></li><li style=\"list-style-type:decimal;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Ci venga data immediata comunicazione di qualsiasi variazione rilevante o Data Breach che coinvolga tale Sub-Responsabile.</span></p></li></ol><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Rimaniamo in attesa di ricevere copia dell&#039;atto di nomina sottoscritto (o conferma dell&#039;avvenuta firma) per l&#039;aggiornamento dei nostri registri privacy.</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Distinti saluti.</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>[Tua Azienda]</strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Il Legale Rappresentante / Responsabile Privacy</span></p><p><br></p>',	1,	NULL,	NULL,	'2026-04-25 08:03:03',	'2026-04-25 08:04:31'),
(6,	'onboarding sub responsabile',	'<h1 style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:24pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Onboarding Sub-Responsabile</strong></span></h1><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:italic;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><em>Il presente verbale attesta l&#039;avvenuta verifica dei requisiti di conformità al GDPR da parte della sub-agenzia esterna prima dell&#039;affidamento delle attività di telemarketing.</em></span></p><h2 style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>1. Anagrafica Sub-Agenzia</strong></span></h2><table style=\"border:none;border-collapse:collapse;\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:0pt;\"><td style=\"border-left:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;border-right:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;border-bottom:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;border-top:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;vertical-align:top;background-color:#f9f9f9;padding:7.5pt 7.5pt 7.5pt 7.5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:7.5pt;margin-bottom:7.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Ragione Sociale:</strong></span>