in-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Autorizzazione Mandante:</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> La mandante (Utility) è stata informata o ha autorizzato il sub-appalto?<br>[ ] Sì [ ] No [ ] In attesa</span></p></li><li style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Sicurezza Logica:</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> La sub-agenzia utilizzerà il CRM/Dialer del Titolare con accessi protetti?<br>[ ] Sì [ ] No (Specificare software terzo)</span></p></li><li style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Misure di Sicurezza:</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> È stata verificata la presenza di firewall, antivirus e policy di password sicure?<br>[ ] Sì [ ] No</span></p></li><li style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Localizzazione:</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> Se extra-UE, sono state sottoscritte le Clausole Contrattuali Standard (SCC)?<br>[ ] Sì [ ] No [ ] N/A (Sede in UE)</span></p></li></ul><h2 style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:11.25pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>3. Adempimenti Contrattuali e Formativi</strong></span></h2><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Si conferma l&#039;avvenuta consegna e sottoscrizione dei seguenti documenti:</span></p><ol style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\" start=\"1\"><li style=\"list-style-type:decimal;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Contratto di nomina a Sub-Responsabile (Art. 28 GDPR):</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> [ ] Firmato</span></p></li><li style=\"list-style-type:decimal;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Manuale Operativo Privacy per Operatori:</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> [ ] Consegnato</span></p></li><li style=\"list-style-type:decimal;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Checklist Privacy Operatore:</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> [ ] Consegnata e affissa nelle postazioni</span></p></li><li style=\"list-style-type:decimal;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Lettera di nomina &quot;Autorizzati al trattamento&quot; (per gli operatori):</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> [ ] Ricevuta lista nominativa</span></p></li></ol><h2 style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:11.25pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>4. Restrizioni Tecniche Applicate</strong></span></h2><ul style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\"><li style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Whitelisting IP:</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> L&#039;accesso ai sistemi è limitato agli indirizzi IP: _____________________</span></p></li><li style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>MFA:</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> È attiva l&#039;autenticazione a due fattori per i supervisori della sub-agenzia? [ ] Sì [ ] No</span></p></li><li style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Registrazioni Audio:</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> La sub-agenzia è autorizzata ad accedere ai file audio? [ ] Solo ascolto [ ] Download [ ] No</span></p></li></ul><h2 style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:11.25pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>5. Esito del Processo di Onboarding</strong></span></h2><p><br></p><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 11.25pt;margin-right: 11.25pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>VALUTAZIONE DEL DPO:</strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 11.25pt;margin-right: 11.25pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">[ ] IDONEA: La sub-agenzia può iniziare le attività.</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 11.25pt;margin-right: 11.25pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">[ ] IDONEA CON RISERVA: Avvio consentito previa risoluzione dei punti: ________________</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 11.25pt;margin-right: 11.25pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">[ ] NON IDONEA.</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Firma DPO (Call Center Titolare): ____________________      Data: _______________</span></p><p><br></p>',	1,	NULL,	NULL,	'2026-04-25 08:19:45',	'2026-04-25 08:19:45'),
(7,	'cessione lead',	'<h1 style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:24pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Accordo di Cessione Dati e Garanzia di Consenso</strong></span></h1><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:italic;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><em>Contratto tra il List Provider (Cedente) e il Committente/Cliente Finale (Cessionario).</em></span></p><h2 style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>1. Oggetto</strong></span></h2><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Il Cedente si impegna a fornire al Cessionario lead qualificati (anagrafiche e consensi) per finalità di marketing/fissaggio appuntamenti.</span></p><h2 style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>2. Garanzia del Consenso</strong></span></h2><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Il Cedente garantisce che ogni singolo dato fornito è corredato da un consenso informato, specifico e documentato, comprensivo dell&#039;autorizzazione alla comunicazione a terzi.</span></p><h2 style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>3. Obblighi del Cessionario (Committente)</strong></span></h2><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Il Cessionario, ricevuti i dati, si impegna a:</span></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\"><li style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Fornire all&#039;interessato la propria informativa privacy al primo contatto utile (Art. 14 GDPR).</span></p></li><li style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Rispettare le volontà dell&#039;interessato in caso di revoca del consenso comunicata direttamente al Cedente.</span></p></li><li style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Non utilizzare i dati per finalità diverse da quelle per cui sono stati raccolti (es. rivendita del lead a terzi).</span></p></li></ul><h2 style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:11.25pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>4. Responsabilità e Manleva</strong></span></h2><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Le parti si danno atto che, dal momento della consegna del file/lead, il Cessionario assume la veste di <strong>Titolare Autonomo</strong>. Il Cedente risponde esclusivamente dell&#039;eventuale invalidità del consenso raccolto all&#039;origine.</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Data: ____________________</span></p><table style=\"border:none;border-collapse:collapse;\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:0pt;\"><td style=\"vertical-align:top;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Firma Cedente (List Provider): ____________________</span></p></td><td style=\"vertical-align:top;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Firma Cessionario (Committente): ____________________</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table>',	1,	NULL,	NULL,	'2026-04-25 08:30:02',	'2026-04-25 09:11:15'),
(8,	'risposta accesso ai dati',	'<h1 style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:24pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Modello di Risposta all&#039;Interessato (Esercizio Diritti)</strong></span></h1><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:italic;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><em>Oggetto: Riscontro alla Sua istanza di esercizio dei diritti in materia di protezione dei dati personali.</em></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Gentile </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>[Nome e Cognome dell&#039;Interessato]</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">,</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">facciamo seguito alla Sua richiesta del [Data Ricevimento] relativa all&#039;esercizio dei diritti previsti dal Regolamento UE 2016/679 (GDPR).</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">In qualità di Titolare/Responsabile del trattamento, Le comunichiamo che abbiamo provveduto a dare seguito alla Sua istanza come segue:</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>[Selezionare l&#039;opzione pertinente:]</strong></span></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\"><li style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>OPZIONE A (Cancellazione/Opposizione):</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> I Suoi dati personali sono stati inseriti nella nostra Blacklist interna. Pertanto, i Suoi recapiti non saranno più oggetto di alcun contatto per finalità commerciali o di marketing da parte dei nostri sistemi e delle nostre reti di vendita.</span></p></li><li style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>OPZIONE B (Accesso ai dati):</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> Le confermiamo che i dati in nostro possesso sono i seguenti: [Elenco dati, es. Nome, Cognome, Telefono]. Tali dati sono stati acquisiti in data [Data] tramite la fonte [Nome Fonte/Portale/Mandante] a seguito del consenso da Lei prestato in pari data.</span></p></li></ul><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Le ricordiamo che, per qualsiasi ulteriore necessità, può contattare il nostro Responsabile della Protezione dei Dati (DPO) all&#039;indirizzo email: [Inserire Email DPO].</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Rimaniamo a Sua disposizione e Le porgiamo distinti saluti.</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>[Nome Società/Call Center]</strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Ufficio Privacy / Back Office</span></p><p><br></p>',	1,	NULL,	NULL,	'2026-04-25 08:35:05',	'2026-04-25 09:11:17'),
(9,	'checklist sw',	'<h1 style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:24pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Checklist Software</strong></span></h1><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:italic;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><em>Da inviare ai fornitori di CRM, Dialer e piattaforme cloud per accertare la conformità alle prescrizioni del Garante Privacy italiano (Provv. 2008 Amministratori di Sistema).</em></span></p><h2 style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>1. Gestione Log di Accesso (Fondamentale)</strong></span></h2><ul style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\"><li style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Registrazione Accessi:</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> Il software registra i log degli accessi (login/logout) effettuati dagli utenti con privilegi di &quot;Amministratore&quot;?<br>[ ] Sì [ ] No</span></p></li><li style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Inalterabilità:</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> I log sono protetti da tentativi di modifica o cancellazione da parte degli amministratori stessi?<br>[ ] Sì [ ] No</span></p></li><li style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Retention:</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> Il sistema garantisce la conservazione dei log per almeno </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>6 mesi</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> come richiesto dal Garante Italiano?<br>[ ] Sì [ ] No</span></p></li><li style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Esportabilità:</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> È possibile esportare i log in formati standard (CSV/PDF) per scopi di audit o controllo?<br>[ ] Sì [ ] No</span></p></li></ul><h2 style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:11.25pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>2. Sicurezza e Controllo Accessi</strong></span></h2><ul style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\"><li style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA):</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> La piattaforma supporta l&#039;autenticazione a due fattori per gli account amministrativi?<br>[ ] Sì [ ] No</span></p></li><li style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Utenze Nominali:</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> Il sistema permette la creazione di utenze amministrative individuali (evitando l&#039;uso di account condivisi &quot;admin/admin&quot;)?<br>[ ] Sì [ ] No</span></p></li><li style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Audit Trail Operativo:</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> Oltre ai login, il sistema registra le operazioni critiche (es. esportazione massiva di lead, cancellazione database)?<br>[ ] Sì [ ] No</span></p></li></ul><h2 style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:11.25pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>3. Localizzazione e Sub-Responsabili</strong></span></h2><ul style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\"><li style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Data Region:</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> In quale regione geografica risiedono i server e i database del servizio? [ ] UE [ ] USA [ ] Altro: _______________</span></p></li><li style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Amministratori di Sistema del Fornitore:</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> Il fornitore garantisce che i propri tecnici che effettuano manutenzione sui server siano debitamente nominati AdS?<br>[ ] Sì [ ] No</span></p></li></ul><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 11.25pt;margin-right: 11.25pt;margin-top:26.25pt;margin-bottom:26.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:#fff3e0;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Nota per il Fornitore:</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:#fff3e0;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> Il mancato rispetto del requisito di conservazione dei log (6 mesi) costituisce una non conformità grave rispetto al Provvedimento del Garante del 27/11/2008 applicabile sul territorio italiano.</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Compilato da: __________________________ Ruolo: __________________________ Data: _______________</span></p><p><br></p>',	1,	NULL,	NULL,	'2026-04-25 08:36:53',	'2026-04-25 08:36:53'),
(10,	'Nomina AdS',	'<h1 style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:24pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Nomina Amministratore Sistema (AdS)</strong></span></h1><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:italic;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><em>Da allegare al contratto di assistenza tecnica/manutenzione informatica tra il Call Center (Titolare) e la Società IT Esterna (Fornitore).</em></span></p><h2 style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>1. Oggetto dell&#039;Addendum</strong></span></h2><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Il presente atto integra il contratto di servizi tra </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>[Ragione Sociale Call Center]</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> (Titolare) e </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>[Ragione Sociale Società IT]</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> (Fornitore), al fine di conformare il rapporto alle prescrizioni del GDPR e del Provvedimento del Garante del 27/11/2008 in materia di Amministratori di Sistema.</span></p><h2 style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>2. Nomina a Responsabile del Trattamento (Art. 28 GDPR)</strong></span></h2><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Il Fornitore è nominato Responsabile Esterno del Trattamento. In tale veste, si impegna a trattare i dati personali dei lead, dei clienti e dei dipendenti del Titolare esclusivamente per le finalità di manutenzione e gestione tecnica dei sistemi (CRM, Dialer, Server).</span></p><h2 style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>3. Funzioni di Amministratore di Sistema (AdS)</strong></span></h2><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Il Fornitore, nell&#039;espletamento dei servizi, svolge funzioni di Amministratore di Sistema. A tal fine, il Fornitore si obbliga a:</span></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\"><li style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Comunicazione Nominativi:</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> Fornire e mantenere aggiornato l&#039;elenco dei propri tecnici incaricati delle attività di amministrazione sui sistemi del Titolare.</span></p></li><li style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Registrazione degli Accessi (Log):</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> Garantire la registrazione degli accessi logici effettuati dai propri tecnici. I log devono contenere: ID utente, data, ora e risorsa acceduta.</span></p></li><li style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Inalterabilità dei Log:</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> Assicurare che i log siano conservati per almeno 6 mesi in modalità inalterabile e protetta da tentativi di manomissione.</span></p></li><li style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -6pt;\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Sicurezza delle Credenziali:</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> Utilizzare metodi di autenticazione forte (MFA) ove disponibili e garantire che ogni tecnico acceda con utenze nominali (divieto di account condivisi).</span></p></li></ul><h2 style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:11.25pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>4. Obbligo di Riservatezza</strong></span></h2><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Il Fornitore garantisce che il personale incaricato delle funzioni di AdS abbia sottoscritto specifici impegni di riservatezza e sia stato adeguatamente formato sulle responsabilità connesse al ruolo.</span></p><h2 style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>5. Diritto di Audit e Ispezione</strong></span></h2><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Il Titolare (o il DPO nominato) ha il diritto di verificare periodicamente, con preavviso di 5 giorni lavorativi, la conformità del Fornitore alle presenti istruzioni, richiedendo estratti dei log o evidenze sulle misure di sicurezza adottate.</span></p><p><br></p><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 11.25pt;margin-right: 11.25pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Dichiarazione del Fornitore:</strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 11.25pt;margin-right: 11.25pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Il Fornitore dichiara di aver preso visione del Provvedimento del Garante del 27/11/2008 e di possedere i requisiti tecnici e organizzativi per ricoprire il ruolo di Amministratore di Sistema Esterno.</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Data: ____________________</span></p><table style=\"border:none;border-collapse:collapse;\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:0pt;\"><td style=\"vertical-align:top;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Firma per il Titolare: ____________________</span></p></td><td style=\"vertical-align:top;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Firma per il Fornitore (AdS Esterno): ____________________</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p><br></p>',	1,	NULL,	NULL,	'2026-04-25 08:38:15',	'2026-04-25 08:38:15'),
(11,	'AdS Audit',	'<h1 style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:24pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Verbale di Verifica Annuale dell&#039;Operato dell&#039;Amministratore di Sistema (AdS)</strong></span></h1><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:italic;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><em>Ai sensi del Provvedimento del Garante Privacy del 27 novembre 2008. Questo documento attesta l&#039;attività di controllo svolta dal Titolare o dal DPO sulla conformità delle attività tecniche.</em></span></p><h2 style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>1. Estremi della Verifica</strong></span></h2><table style=\"border:none;border-collapse:collapse;\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:0pt;\"><td style=\"border-left:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;border-right:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;border-bottom:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;border-top:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;vertical-align:top;background-color:#f9f9f9;padding:7.5pt 7.5pt 7.5pt 7.5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:7.5pt;margin-bottom:7.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Amministratore Verificato:</strong></span></p></td><td style=\"border-left:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;border-right:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;border-bottom:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;border-top:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;vertical-align:top;padding:7.5pt 7.5pt 7.5pt 7.5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:7.5pt;margin-bottom:7.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">[Nome e Cognome]</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:0pt;\"><td style=\"border-left:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;border-right:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;border-bottom:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;border-top:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;vertical-align:top;background-color:#f9f9f9;padding:7.5pt 7.5pt 7.5pt 7.5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:7.5pt;margin-bottom:7.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Data della Verifica:</strong></span></p></td><td style=\"border-left:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;border-right:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;border-bottom:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;border-top:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;vertical-align:top;padding:7.5pt 7.5pt 7.5pt 7.5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:7.5pt;margin-bottom:7.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">[Inserire Data]</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:0pt;\"><td style=\"border-left:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;border-right:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;border-bottom:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;border-top:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;vertical-align:top;background-color:#f9f9f9;padding:7.5pt 7.5pt 7.5pt 7.5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:7.5pt;margin-bottom:7.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Soggetto Verificatore:</strong></span></p></td><td style=\"border-left:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;border-right:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;border-bottom:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;border-top:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;vertical-align:top;padding:7.5pt 7.5pt 7.5pt 7.5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:7.5pt;margin-bottom:7.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">[DPO / Rappresentante Legale]</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><h2 style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:11.25pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>2. Oggetto del Controllo</strong></span></h2><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">La verifica è stata condotta per accertare la rispondenza dell&#039;attività dell&#039;AdS alle istruzioni impartite nell&#039;atto di nomina:</span></p><table style=\"border:none;border-collapse:collapse;\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:0pt;\"><th style=\"border-left:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;border-right:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;border-bottom:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;border-top:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;vertical-align:top;background-color:#f2f2f2;padding:7.5pt 7.5pt 7.5pt 7.5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:7.5pt;margin-bottom:7.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Ambito di Verifica</span></p></th><th style=\"border-left:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;border-right:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;border-bottom:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;border-top:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;vertical-align:top;background-color:#f2f2f2;padding:7.5pt 7.5pt 7.5pt 7.5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:7.5pt;margin-bottom:7.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Esito</span></p></th><th style=\"border-left:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;border-right:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;border-bottom:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;border-top:solid #dddddd 0.75pt;vertical-align:top;background-color:#f2f2f2;padding:7.5pt 7.5pt 7.5pt 7.5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:7.5pt;margin-bottom:7.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:n